descriptionHTML:
Jazz defines the 20th Century and it's clearly one of the best choices to listen while you work on your device...

With myTuner Jazz you will get 50 elegant jazz songs to listen when you want (even if you don't have internet connection).

You will be able to:
- Have access to more than 50 elegant jazz songs to listen when you want
- Select and listen to more than 250 different internet radios that are broadcasting jazz music, searchable by country
- Check the top selling jazz music songs per country each day, so you can listen to a preview and check if you want to buy it
- Add to favorite songs and radios you like for faster access
- Record radio stations
- Listen to music in the background, so you can work
- Use AirPlay for a better sound experience
